==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Teledu
<hw>Tel"e*du</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An
East Indian carnivore (<spn>Mydaus meliceps</spn>) allied to the badger,
and noted for the very offensive odor that it emits, somewhat resembling
that of a skunk. It is a native of the high mountains of Java and
Sumatra, and has long, silky fur. Called also <altname>stinking
badger</altname>, and <altname>stinkard</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Telega</ent>⟦br⟧
